<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Barangay Clearance</title>
  <style>
    /* Set the page size for printing */
    @page {
      size: 8.5in 11in; /* Set paper size to 8.5 x 11 inches (short bond paper) */
      margin: 2cm; /* Set margin for print */
    }

    @media print {
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;

      }

      .print-button {
        display: none; /* Hide the print button during printing */
      }

    }


    .header {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-evenly;
    }

    .header img{
      width: 80px;
    }

    .header-text{
      text-align: center;
      
    }

    .header-text p{
      margin: 0;
    }

    body{
      font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; /* Consistent font family */
    }


    .content {
      
      font-size: 18px; /* Standard font size */
      margin: 20px; /* Margin for the content */
    }

    .certificate-title {
      text-align: center; /* Center-align the certificate title */
      font-size: 2em; /* Larger font size for the certificate title */
      font-weight: bold; /* Make it bold */
      text-transform: uppercase; /* Make it uppercase */
      text-decoration: underline;
      margin-top: 100px; /* Extra margin at the top */
      margin-bottom: 100px; /* Extra margin at the top */

    }

    .certificate-body {
      text-align: justify; /* Justify the text for a clean layout */
      line-height: 1.5; /* Spacing between lines */
      text-indent: 20px;
    }

    .certificate-signature{
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-end;
      margin-right: 30px;
      margin-top: 80px;
    }

    .certificate-signature p{
      margin: 0;
    }

    .certificate-signature .content{
      text-align: start;
    }

    .footer{
      border-bottom: 2px solid black;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 14px;
      padding-left: 10px;
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 100%;
    }


    .print-button {
      text-align: center; /* Center-align the button */
      margin-top: 20px; /* Add margin at the top */
    }

    .print-button button {
      padding: 10px 20px; /* Padding for the button */
      background-color: #4CAF50; /* Green background */
      color: white; /* White text */
      border: none; /* No border */
      border-radius: 5px; /* Rounded corners */
      font-size: 1em; /* Font size */
      cursor: pointer; /* Cursor changes to pointer */
    }

    .print-button button:hover {
      background-color: #45a049; /* Darker shade on hover */
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div>
      <img src="/images/admin-image/sideLogoBrgy.png" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="header-text">
      <p>REPUBLIC OF THE PHILIPPINES</p>
      <p>BARANGAY 496 ZONE 49</p>
      <p>District IV â€“ Manila</p>
      <p>OFFICE OF THE BARANGAY CHAIRMAN</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img src="/images/admin-image/sideLogoMunicapality.png" alt="">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="certificate-title">Barangay Clearance</div> <!-- Certificate title -->
    
    <div class="certificate-body">
      This is to certify that <strong><%= matchingRequest.name.replace(/\./g, '') %></strong> is a resident of this barangay, presently residing at <strong><%= UserFullInformation.address %></strong> is known to be of good moral character ang law abiding citizen in the community
      <br><br>
      This certification is being issued upon the request of  the above  named  for
        whatever  purpose  it  may  serve.  Any help  extended  to  him/her  will be  highly
        appreciated by the undersigned.

      <br><br>
      NOTE: for <strong>><%= matchingRequest.purpose %></strong> purposes only..
    </div>
    <div class="certificate-signature">
      <div class="content">
        <p>Very truly yours,</p>
        <br>
        <br>
        <br>
        <br>
        <p>EDMOND B. DELA PAZ</p>
        <p>Barangay Chairman</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      Note: Not valid if no official seal and signature of Barangay Chairman
    </div>
  </div>


  <script>window.print()</script>
</body>
</html>
